#: ../../../../release/_9.5-stripped.md:309
msgid ""
"The `scnlib` third-party library (v4.0.1) has been added to VTK for fast and "
"efficient parsing of numbers from strings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.5-stripped.md:311
#: ../../../../release/_9.5-stripped.md:657
msgid "WebAssembly"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.5-stripped.md:313
msgid "**Allow binding a WASM scene manager render window to a HTML canvas**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.5-stripped.md:315
msgid ""
"You can now call `sceneManager.bindRenderWindow(vtkTypeUInt32 id, const "
"char* canvasSelector)` method from JavaScript   in order to bind a render "
"window to a HTML canvas element."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.5-stripped.md:318
msgid "**Add exception support for WebAssembly builds**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.5-stripped.md:320
msgid ""
"You can now enable exceptions in VTK wasm build with the "
"`VTK_WEBASSEMBLY_EXCEPTIONS` option. Default value is `OFF`."
msgstr ""

